, Puerto Peñasco (
<collectingRegion box="[780,866,1768,1794]" country="Mexico" name="Sonora" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">Sonora</collectingRegion>
)
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="12" lastPageNumber="213" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="11.[136,1452,1662,2076]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,335,1803,1829]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">Remarks:—</emphasis>
Specimens of this species were previously identified as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Setchell &amp; Gardner" authorityYear="1924" box="[992,1136,1803,1829]" class="Phaeophyceae" family="Sargassaceae" genus="Sargassum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Fucales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="johnstonii">
<emphasis box="[992,1006,1803,1829]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1024,1136,1803,1829]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">johnstonii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the field. After detailed morphological assessment we found that these specimens shared some characteristics with both 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Setchell &amp; Gardner" authorityYear="1924" box="[1237,1402,1838,1864]" class="Phaeophyceae" family="Sargassaceae" genus="Sargassum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Fucales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="lapazeanum">
<emphasis box="[1237,1251,1838,1864]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1267,1402,1838,1864]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">lapazeanum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Setchell &amp; Gardner" authorityYear="1924" box="[136,277,1873,1900]" class="Phaeophyceae" family="Sargassaceae" genus="Sargassum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Fucales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="johnstonii">
<emphasis box="[136,150,1874,1900]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[165,277,1873,1899]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">johnstonii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, suggesting that these specimens belong to the same section; also there are some similar morphologies. In 
<collectingCountry box="[168,278,1908,1935]" name="China" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">East Asia</collectingCountry>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Kuntze, O." box="[291,455,1908,1935]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" pagination="191 - 239" refId="ref13687" refString="Kuntze, O. (1880) Revision von Sargassum und das sogennante Sargasso-Meer. Botanische Jahrbucher fur Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie 1: 191 - 239." type="journal article" year="1880">Kuntze (1880)</bibRefCitation>
reported some specimens similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="(Mertens ex Roth 1800: 104) Kuntze (1880: 215" authorityName="Kuntze" authorityYear="1880" baseAuthorityName="Mertens ex Roth" baseAuthorityPageNumber="104" baseAuthorityYear="1800" class="Phaeophyceae" family="Sargassaceae" genus="Sargassum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Fucales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="thunbergii">
<emphasis box="[876,890,1909,1935]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[905,1021,1908,1934]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">thunbergii</emphasis>
(Mertens ex Roth 1800: 104) 
<bibRefCitation author="Kuntze, O." pageId="11" pageNumber="212" pagination="191 - 239" refId="ref13687" refString="Kuntze, O. (1880) Revision von Sargassum und das sogennante Sargasso-Meer. Botanische Jahrbucher fur Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie 1: 191 - 239." type="journal article" year="1880">Kuntze (1880: 215</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 228); however, specimens from the Gulf of California were different and none of the characteristics could be applied to characterize the 
<specimenCount box="[474,627,1979,2006]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" type="generic">25 specimens</specimenCount>
collected prior to molecular analysis. Both molecular and morphological analyses indicated that these specimens belong to a distinct entity which we propose to describe as a new species under the name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="G. Andrade-Sorcia &amp; S. M. Boo" authorityYear="2014" box="[245,335,2049,2076]" class="Phaeophyceae" family="Sargassaceae" genus="Sargassum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Fucales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="ulixei">
<emphasis box="[245,259,2050,2076]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[273,335,2049,2075]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">ulixei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5150062" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5150062" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5150062/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="213" startId="12.[136,229,1511,1533]" targetBox="[363,1229,201,1486]" targetPageId="12">
<paragraph blockId="12.[136,1452,1511,1569]" pageId="12" pageNumber="213">
